app.containers.IcoList.analyzerContent: Monetha’s and ICO’s Analyzer aggregates and analyzes the main information about ICOs to estimate the amount of funds they have raised. It then stores the data in a decentralized reputation passport on the blockchain. This allows anyone interested to verify an ICO's performance in an objective and censorship-resistant manner. The project showcases Monetha Reputation Framework–its Payments and Reputation layers–in action.
app.containers.IcoList.analyzerFooter: The information contained on this website is provided for informative purposes and should not be considered as investment or any other kind of advice or recommendation.
